<Link id="l00657" /><CodeLine lineNumber="657"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Emit the largest nop instruction smaller than or equal to \\p NumBytes</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00658" /><CodeLine lineNumber="658"><Highlight kind="comment">/// bytes.  Return the size of nop emitted.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00659" /><CodeLine lineNumber="659" lineLink="#ab371721ad31c3a0d4e5eb8fce0e8a13a"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">static</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">unsigned</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> <a href="#ab371721ad31c3a0d4e5eb8fce0e8a13a">emitNop</a>(<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mcstreamer">MCStreamer</a> &amp;OS, </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">unsigned</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> NumBytes,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00660" /><CodeLine lineNumber="660"><Highlight kind="normal">                        </Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">const</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/x86subtarget">X86Subtarget</a> &#42;Subtarget) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00661" /><CodeLine lineNumber="661"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Determine the longest nop which can be efficiently decoded for the given</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00662" /><CodeLine lineNumber="662"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// target cpu.  15-bytes is the longest single NOP instruction, but some</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00663" /><CodeLine lineNumber="663"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// platforms can&#39;t decode the longest forms efficiently.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00664" /><CodeLine lineNumber="664"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">unsigned</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> MaxNopLength = 1;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00665" /><CodeLine lineNumber="665"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">if</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (Subtarget-&gt;is64Bit()) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00666" /><CodeLine lineNumber="666"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// FIXME: We can use NOOPL on 32-bit targets with FeatureNOPL, but the</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00667" /><CodeLine lineNumber="667"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// IndexReg/BaseReg below need to be updated.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00668" /><CodeLine lineNumber="668"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">if</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (Subtarget-&gt;hasFeature(X86::TuningFast7ByteNOP))</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00669" /><CodeLine lineNumber="669"><Highlight kind="normal">      MaxNopLength = 7;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00670" /><CodeLine lineNumber="670"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">else</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">if</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (Subtarget-&gt;hasFeature(X86::TuningFast15ByteNOP))</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00671" /><CodeLine lineNumber="671"><Highlight kind="normal">      MaxNopLength = 15;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00672" /><CodeLine lineNumber="672"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">else</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">if</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (Subtarget-&gt;hasFeature(X86::TuningFast11ByteNOP))</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00673" /><CodeLine lineNumber="673"><Highlight kind="normal">      MaxNopLength = 11;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00674" /><CodeLine lineNumber="674"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">else</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00675" /><CodeLine lineNumber="675"><Highlight kind="normal">      MaxNopLength = 10;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00676" /><CodeLine lineNumber="676"><Highlight kind="normal">  &#125; </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">if</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (Subtarget-&gt;is32Bit())</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00677" /><CodeLine lineNumber="677"><Highlight kind="normal">    MaxNopLength = 2;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00678" /><CodeLine lineNumber="678"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00679" /><CodeLine lineNumber="679"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// Cap a single nop emission at the profitable value for the target</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00680" /><CodeLine lineNumber="680"><Highlight kind="normal">  NumBytes = std::min(NumBytes, MaxNopLength);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00681" /><CodeLine lineNumber="681"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
